# Blindspot Tracker environment variables
#
# The app itself reads only static JSON in /data, so NO environment variables
# are required to run or deploy it.
#
# The real-data ingestion script (npm run fetch-data) uses the GDELT DOC 2.0
# API, which is free and requires NO API key — so nothing is needed here for
# live data either.
#
# This file documents where a Ground News dataset/API key WOULD go if access
# is granted, so the pipeline can be upgraded from the GDELT proxy to Ground
# News' first-party cross-spectrum coverage data.
#
# GROUND_NEWS_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
# GROUND_NEWS_API_BASE=https://api.ground.news

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Real coverage data via NewsData.io (npm run fetch-newsdata)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Alternative to GDELT for real coverage volume. Free key: https://newsdata.io/register
# Free tier sees only the last 48h, so each run fills the current week; re-run
# periodically to accumulate real history. Not needed for GDELT (npm run fetch-data).
#
# NEWSDATA_API_KEY=pub_xxxxxxxx

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Per-article bias analyzer (/analyze)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The analyzer is provider-agnostic: it calls any OpenAI-compatible
# /chat/completions endpoint. WITHOUT a key it still works, falling back to a
# shallow keyword heuristic (clearly labeled in the UI).
#
# Set LLM_API_KEY to enable real article-level analysis. Examples:
#   OpenAI:     LLM_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1        LLM_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
#   OpenRouter: LLM_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1     LLM_MODEL=anthropic/claude-3.5-sonnet
#   Groq:       LLM_BASE_URL=https://api.groq.com/openai/v1   LLM_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile
#   Ollama:     LLM_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434/v1        LLM_MODEL=llama3.1   (LLM_API_KEY=ollama)
#
# LLM_API_KEY=your_llm_api_key_here
# LLM_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
# LLM_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
